{
  "stem": "27509.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I picked up my index with the photograph on the left inside page, underneath my photograph was a rubber stamp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that stamp said that my place is reserved on the left side of the lecture hall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In other words, by law of the university, we were not allowed to sit on the same benches as our Polish colleagues.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was a ghetto within the university classroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Jewish students who would not submit to that rule used to stand at the back wall, supporting the wall, and taking notes standing up, standing up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had the temerity, or the folly, one day to come into a class and sit on the right side of the hall, defying [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the regulations.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A youthful folly is [INAUDIBLE] is doing all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was told later on, because I went to talk to the professor, somebody came in and told me to try and stay and engage the man for as long as I can, because outside on the stairs, the students are standing on both sides of the staircase, waiting for me to come down, to beat me up.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And much to my delight, the professor was so responsive, the more questions I threw at him, the more he got involved.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they got sick and tired of waiting for me, and they dispersed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And by the time I came out, there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The reaction was not a-- it was very chilling, but not altogether unexpected, because I remember that every time I used to walk through the iron gate of the university campus of Warsaw, which was at the most beautiful part of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a magnificent city, a magnificent European city.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
